{"tid":617813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"遇韓男失知覺醒來赤裸在床 女子疑遭強姦","createTime":"2018-04-05T09:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T09:33:20.000Z","uid":153663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5185c20ba6055f37fc30059e077b6d2ba7e05f4d","tid":617813,"uid":153663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=nHGlubfLw6K5TswqfdeYR54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bfa76587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】一名女子在夜店結識南韓遊客後，疑無故失去知覺，翌晨起床發現自己和韓男雙雙赤裸睡在床上，始憶起疑遭對方強姦，於是報警。南韓青年事後被控一項強姦罪，今(4日)被解往九龍城法院提訊，暫毋須答辯。裁判官將案件押後至5月2日再訊，以待控方索取法律意見，期間被告准以10萬港元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n22歲被告Park Jaehoon報稱侍應，被控於本月1日，在紅磡一間酒店內強姦女子X。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方反對被告擔保，指酒店閉路電視拍下被告和X返回酒店的情況。裁判官看過閉路電視截圖後，指截圖顯示兩人在走廊傾談，決定批准辯方保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}